Description:

Ever want to monitor your ever changing W.A.N. (wide are network) IP address and have the new emailed to you?  This script does that.  

Example Usage:

/usr/bin/python3.4 /full/path/to/checkip.py 

This works very well with a cron job.

VERY IMPORTANT

This only works with a Gmail accounts.  You must enable third part applications to have access to your account.

Follow this URL for information on how to enable this.

https://www.google.com/settings/security/lesssecureapps
